rpersonal drawbacks that could impair crew cooperation (B). Therefore, I consider Candidate\u202fC the strongest overall fit for the long\u2011distance pilot role.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_2\", \"vote\": \"Candidate C\"}"}
